WEBVTT

00:09:28.995 --> 00:09:30.440
for bigger disputes,

00:09:30.464 --> 00:09:34.018
such as the Parthenon Marbles,
claimed by Greece.

00:09:34.574 --> 00:09:37.043
After visiting the five museums,

00:09:37.067 --> 00:09:40.867
Octavius returned home
to his people empty-handed.

00:09:42.284 --> 00:09:43.594
He later told me,

00:09:43.618 --> 00:09:46.919
"It hurts my heart to see
the Ahayu:da so far away.

00:09:46.943 --> 00:09:48.617
They all belong together.

00:09:49.066 --> 00:09:53.344
It's like a family member
that's missing from a family dinner.

00:09:54.292 --> 00:09:57.716
When one is gone,
their strength is broken."

00:09:58.848 --> 00:10:01.662
I wish that my colleagues
in Europe and beyond